  m_Name: NeighborJournal_11
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::JournalData
  id: 28
  title: "Nh\u1EADt k\xFD h\xE0ng x\xF3m #11 \u2014 Ch\u1EE7 qu\xE1n ph\u1EDF"
  category: 3
  content: "Ng\xE0y m\u1EDF qu\xE1n cu\u1ED1i c\xF9ng: 12 th\xE1ng 3. Kh\xE1ch v\u1EAFng
    d\u1EA7n t\u1EEB h\xF4m c\xF3 tin d\u1ECBch. T\xF4i n\u1EA5u n\u1ED3i ph\u1EDF
    cu\u1ED1i cho m\u1EA5y \xF4ng h\xE0ng x\xF3m gi\xE0. \u0102n xong ai c\u0169ng
    kh\xF3c. T\xF4i \u0111\u1EC3 l\u1EA1i n\u1ED3i n\u01B0\u1EDBc d\xF9ng c\xF2n
    \u0111un nh\u1ECF l\u1EEDa, m\u1EA5y kg th\u1ECBt trong t\u1EE7 \u0111\xF4ng.
    Ai \u0111\xF3 n\u1EBFu c\xF2n s\u1ED1ng, c\u1EE9 \u0103n. Kh\xF4ng ai thu ti\u1EC1n
    n\u1EEFa \u0111\xE2u. Qu\xE1n m\u1EDF c\u1EEDa t\u1EF1 do."
  image: {fileID: 0}
  voiceLog: {fileID: 0}
